descriptions.value: In his 'Wealth Acquisition Specialist' application form, Number K wrote the letter 'K' in every number field, but his talent with handguns made him more than qualified for the position. Number K keeps the details of his life private—none of his colleagues have seen his face—making him one of The Professionals' most feared heist managers. Don't count us down. Just say go.
Patch: Team Liquid | Stockholm 2021

markethashname: Sir Bloody Skullhead Darryl | The Professionals
marketname: Sir Bloody Skullhead Darryl | The Professionals

descriptions.value: The leader of 'The Professionals' can be described as cocky, wisecracking, and scarily indifferent with regards to the suffering of others. He would say he's just a bloke—a bloke that likes to have a bit of fun on the weekend with the local armed tax collectors. He downplays the severity of any heavy situations that come his way, even if he's the last man standing, riddled with bullets, with only seconds left to blow the safe. This black mask has been painted with a white skull, a useful bit of intimidation back when The Professionals were just getting started. Are we gonna bloody finish this thing or what?!
Patch: Metal Silver, Bloodhound

With a smaller magazine than its unmuffled counterpart, the silenced M4A1 provides quieter shots with less recoil and better accuracy. It has been painted with dark green metallic paint and uses a crystallizing mask to create a pattern. Everyone wants to make an impact

A fan favorite from Counter-Strike Source, the Silenced USP Pistol has a detachable silencer that gives shots less recoil while suppressing attention-getting noise. A custom paint job featuring a green monster and other icons inspired by popular urban art has been applied. The silencer has a pearlescent finish. X__X
Powerful and reliable, the AK-47 is one of the most popular assault rifles in the world. It is most deadly in short, controlled bursts of fire. It has been given a laminate stock.
Sticker: Stewie2K | Berlin 2019, Stewie2K | Berlin 2019, Stewie2K | Berlin 2019, Team Liquid | Berlin 2019

High risk and high reward, the infamous AWP is recognizable by its signature report and one-shot, one-kill policy. It has been painted with the image of a skull and roots using high-durability enamel paints. There are some roots you don't want to take hold
Sticker: Stone Scales (Foil), Stone Scales (Foil)

A less expensive option among the terrorist-exclusive assault rifles, the Galil AR is a serviceable weapon in medium to long-range combat. A spray-painted, blue wave pattern sits atop a maroon base. Westward breaks

The R8 Revolver delivers a highly accurate and powerful round at the expense of a lengthy trigger-pull. Firing rapidly by fanning the hammer may be the best option when point-blank stopping power is required. A multicolored pattern of various Phoenix Connexion graffiti has been applied. "They cannot stop us now!"

A fully automatic variant of the CZ75, the CZ75-Auto is the ideal short-term choice for turning the tables and gaining your opponents weapon. But with very little ammo in the magazine, strong trigger discipline is required. It has heat-transferred decals applied to a white and green base. For a better tomorrow
Sticker: Drug War Veteran

More accurate but less damaging than its AK-47 counterpart, the M4A4 is the full-auto assault rifle of choice for CTs. It has been custom painted with a dark blue base and red spider lilies above the magazine and trigger. Bright colors are a warning, not an invitation

This Music Kit will replace all of the music in the game and is shareable with anyone you are playing with. It also includes an MVP Anthem that plays for everyone in the match when you are MVP.

The Music Kit replaces the following music:
- Main Menu
- Round Start and End
- Map Objective
- Ten Second Warning
- Death Camera
